{"tid":1626922,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人權法不斷加辣，但好似加錯哂方向，咁樣係永遠嬴唔到","createTime":"2019-10-05T13:39:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T14:12:35.000Z","uid":21699,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e55151c1ee208a3ea54e01e5378ba7a99b6a1309","tid":1626922,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:39:48.000Z","msg":"大專遊說緊制裁埋直系家屬，聽落好似好激奮人心<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但如果大家真心想嬴，係咪應該遊說加入呢條「在202x年前實行真普選，否則取消關係法」呢？<br />\n<br />\n以我所知，現時人權法只係要求積極推動香港2020年有普選，但完全冇寫過如果冇普選會有咩後果，簡稱，完全可以ignore。<br />\n<br />\n加辣制栽埋直系家屬，的確係興奮。但如果想嬴，普選先係關鍵。點解呢個加辣方向完全冇人提及？"},{"pid":"43bd1725ba36c3dca43e76a14b2bccc09b01c5bd","tid":1626922,"uid":263186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"佢話每年會「調查」香港人權咩情況<br />\n有問題就考慮仲需唔需要關係法"},{"pid":"3dd315e396e04645e0dbcfec5671b67217d6bba0","tid":1626922,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43bd1725ba36c3dca43e76a14b2bccc09b01c5bd","tid":1626922,"uid":263186,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:49:15.000Z","msg":"佢話每年會「調查」香港人權咩情況<br />\n有問題就考慮仲需唔需要關係法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:50:43.000Z","msg":"可惜呢個唔係一個obligatory measures to push democratic reform"},{"pid":"3c6da7e6b00834fcd569df8eefb51f904eb828b0","tid":1626922,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:52:41.000Z","msg":"我tweet 左所羅門同佢講呢單野"},{"pid":"a32450ed2d95cc26b65e6df065f93d85776ad014","tid":1626922,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:55:09.000Z","msg":"同意請推，比遊說派睇到"},{"pid":"9df0b08cca1e1441c45305ecdc5bdc1f94f68f3e","tid":1626922,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T13:56:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f46547b0123ce22b2b3895fd9734516f6dd9fd87","tid":1626922,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c6da7e6b00834fcd569df8eefb51f904eb828b0","tid":1626922,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score